caption.p: Effects of rFIP-mco on cell migration and invasion. Transwell migration assay (A) and cell migration monitored by the wound healing assay (B) were conducted in A549 cells treated with different concentrations of rFIP-mco. Transwell migration assay (C) and cell migration monitored by the wound healing assay (D) were carried out in HepG2 cells treated with different concentrations of rFIP-mco. * P < 0.05 vs. control groups (untreated cells).
